msgid "What is BMI?"
msgstr "Wat is BMI?"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/anorexic_bmi_calculator.html:320
msgid ""
"Body Mass Index (BMI) is a measure calculated from your weight and height. "
"It's used as a screening tool to identify potential weight-related health "
"issues. The formula is:"
msgstr ""
"Body Mass Index (BMI) is een maatstaf die wordt berekend op basis van uw "
"gewicht en lengte. Het wordt gebruikt als screeningsinstrument om potentiële"
" gewichtsgerelateerde gezondheidsproblemen te identificeren. De formule is:"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/anorexic_bmi_calculator.html:326
msgid ""
"While BMI is a useful screening tool, it doesn't directly measure body fat "
"or account for muscle mass, bone density, or other factors. For very low BMI"
" ranges, it's particularly important to consult healthcare professionals."
msgstr ""
"Hoewel BMI een nuttig screeningsinstrument is, meet het niet rechtstreeks "
"het lichaamsvet en houdt het geen rekening met spiermassa, botdichtheid of "
"andere factoren. Voor zeer lage BMI-waarden is het bijzonder belangrijk om "
"beroepsbeoefenaren in de gezondheidszorg te raadplegen."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/anorexic_bmi_calculator.html:332
msgid "Anorexia-Related BMI Ranges"
msgstr "Anorexia-gerelateerde BMI-bereiken"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/anorexic_bmi_calculator.html:335
msgid "Severe Anorexia: BMI &lt; 15"
msgstr "Ernstige anorexia: BMI &lt; 15"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/anorexic_bmi_calculator.html:337
msgid ""
"This indicates severe underweight status. Immediate medical attention is "
"strongly recommended."
msgstr ""
"Dit wijst op een ernstige ondergewichtstatus. Onmiddellijke medische "
"aandacht wordt sterk aanbevolen."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/anorexic_bmi_calculator.html:341
msgid "Anorexia: BMI 15-17.5"
msgstr "Anorexia: BMI 15-17,5"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/anorexic_bmi_calculator.html:343
msgid ""
"This range falls below the DSM-5 threshold for anorexia nervosa (BMI &lt; "
"17.5). Professional evaluation is recommended."
msgstr ""
"Dit bereik valt onder de DSM-5-drempel voor anorexia nervosa (BMI < 17,5). "
"Professionele evaluatie wordt aanbevolen."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/anorexic_bmi_calculator.html:347
msgid "Underweight: BMI 17.5-18.5"
msgstr "Ondergewicht: BMI 17,5-18,5"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/anorexic_bmi_calculator.html:349
msgid ""
"Below the normal weight range. Consider consulting a healthcare provider to "
"ensure adequate nutrition."
msgstr ""
"Onder het normale gewichtsbereik. Overweeg om een ​​zorgverlener te "
"raadplegen om voor adequate voeding te zorgen."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/anorexic_bmi_calculator.html:353
msgid "Normal: BMI ≥ 18.5"
msgstr "Normaal: BMI ≥ 18,5"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/anorexic_bmi_calculator.html:355
msgid ""
"Within the healthy weight range. Continue maintaining a balanced diet and "
"regular physical activity."
msgstr ""
"Binnen het gezonde gewichtsbereik. Ga door met het handhaven van een "
"uitgebalanceerd dieet en regelmatige lichamelijke activiteit."

