#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_type_calculator.html:272
msgid "What are Body Types?"
msgstr "Wat zijn lichaamstypes?"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_type_calculator.html:274
msgid ""
"Body types, also known as somatotypes, are classifications of human body "
"shapes based on skeletal frame size and body composition. The three main "
"body types are ectomorph, mesomorph, and endomorph, originally proposed by "
"psychologist William Sheldon in the 1940s."
msgstr ""
"Lichaamstypes, ook wel somatotypes genoemd, zijn classificaties van "
"menselijke lichaamsvormen op basis van de skeletgrootte en "
"lichaamssamenstelling. De drie belangrijkste lichaamstypen zijn ectomorf, "
"mesomorf en endomorf, oorspronkelijk voorgesteld door psycholoog William "
"Sheldon in de jaren veertig."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/body_type_calculator.html:277
msgid ""
"While everyone is unique, understanding your body type can help you make "
"informed decisions about nutrition, exercise, and fitness goals that work "
"best with your natural body structure."
msgstr ""
"Hoewel iedereen uniek is, kan het begrijpen van uw lichaamstype u helpen "
"weloverwogen beslissingen te nemen over voeding, lichaamsbeweging en "
"fitnessdoelen die het beste bij uw natuurlijke lichaamsstructuur passen."

