msgstr "Calculator voor dagelijkse eiwitbehoeften"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:7
msgid ""
"Calculate your daily protein needs based on body weight, activity level, and"
" fitness goals. Get personalized protein recommendations."
msgstr ""
"Bereken uw dagelijkse eiwitbehoefte op basis van lichaamsgewicht, "
"activiteitenniveau en fitnessdoelen. Ontvang gepersonaliseerde "
"eiwitaanbevelingen."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:10
msgid ""
"protein calculator, daily protein, protein needs, protein intake, muscle "
"building protein"
msgstr ""
"eiwitcalculator, dagelijkse eiwitten, eiwitbehoeften, eiwitinname, "
"spieropbouwende eiwitten"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:14
msgid "Calculate Daily Protein Needs"
msgstr "Bereken de dagelijkse eiwitbehoeften"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:15
msgid ""
"Calculate your daily protein needs based on body weight, activity level, and"
" fitness goals."
msgstr ""
"Bereken uw dagelijkse eiwitbehoefte op basis van lichaamsgewicht, "
"activiteitenniveau en fitnessdoelen."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:24
msgid "Calculate daily protein needs based on body weight and activity level"
msgstr ""
"Bereken de dagelijkse eiwitbehoefte op basis van lichaamsgewicht en "
"activiteitenniveau"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:51
msgid ""
"Calculate your daily protein needs based on body weight, activity level, and"
" fitness goals. Get personalized protein recommendations and meal "
"distribution."
msgstr ""
"Bereken uw dagelijkse eiwitbehoefte op basis van lichaamsgewicht, "
"activiteitenniveau en fitnessdoelen. Ontvang gepersonaliseerde "
"eiwitaanbevelingen en maaltijddistributie."

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/protein_calculator.html:103
msgid "Little/no exercise"
