#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bra_size_calculator.html:125
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bra_size_calculator.html:666
msgid "How do I measure my bra size?"
msgstr "Hoe meet ik mijn bh-maat?"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bra_size_calculator.html:128
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bra_size_calculator.html:668
msgid ""
"Measure your underbust (ribcage) snugly around your torso, and your bust at "
"the fullest point. The difference between these measurements determines your"
" cup size, while your underbust measurement determines your band size."
msgstr ""
"Meet uw onderborst (ribbenkast) strak rond uw torso, en uw buste op het "
"volste punt. Het verschil tussen deze maten bepaalt je cupmaat, terwijl je "
"onderborstmaat je bandmaat bepaalt."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bra_size_calculator.html:133
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bra_size_calculator.html:672
msgid "What is a sister size?"
msgstr "Wat is een zustermaat?"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bra_size_calculator.html:136
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bra_size_calculator.html:674
msgid ""
"Sister sizes are bra sizes with the same cup volume but different band and "
"cup combinations. For example, 34C, 32D, and 36B are sister sizes. They can "
"be useful if your regular size is not available."
msgstr ""
"Zustermaten zijn bh-maten met hetzelfde cupvolume maar verschillende band- "
"en cupcombinaties. 34C, 32D en 36B zijn bijvoorbeeld zustermaten. Ze kunnen "
"handig zijn als uw normale maat niet beschikbaar is."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bra_size_calculator.html:141
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bra_size_calculator.html:678
msgid "How do I convert between US and UK bra sizes?"
msgstr "Hoe wissel ik tussen Amerikaanse en Britse bh-maten?"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bra_size_calculator.html:144
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bra_size_calculator.html:680
msgid ""
"US and UK bra sizes use the same band sizes, but cup sizes differ after D. "
"US uses D, DD, DDD, G, H, while UK uses D, DD, E, F, FF, G, GG, H. Use our "
"size conversion tool for accurate conversions."
msgstr ""
"Amerikaanse en Britse bh-maten gebruiken dezelfde bandmaten, maar cupmaten "
"verschillen na D. US gebruikt D, DD, DDD, G, H, terwijl UK D, DD, E, F, FF, "
"G, GG, H gebruikt. Gebruik onze maatconversietool voor nauwkeurige "
"conversies."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bra_size_calculator.html:149
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bra_size_calculator.html:684
msgid "What is the difference between band size and cup size?"
msgstr "Wat is het verschil tussen bandmaat en cupmaat?"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bra_size_calculator.html:152
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bra_size_calculator.html:686
msgid ""
"Band size is the measurement around your ribcage (underbust), typically "
"28-50. Cup size is determined by the difference between your bust and band "
"measurements, ranging from AA to N."
msgstr ""
"De bandmaat is de maat rond uw ribbenkast (onderborst), meestal 28-50. De "
"cupmaat wordt bepaald door het verschil tussen uw buste- en bandomvang, "
"variërend van AA tot N."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bra_size_calculator.html:157
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bra_size_calculator.html:690
msgid "Should I measure with or without a bra?"
msgstr "Moet ik met of zonder bh meten?"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bra_size_calculator.html:160
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bra_size_calculator.html:692
msgid ""
"For the most accurate measurement, wear a non-padded, well-fitting bra. The "
"bra should not add extra volume. Measure your underbust snugly and your bust"
" at the fullest point while wearing the bra."
msgstr ""
"Voor de meest nauwkeurige meting draagt ​​u een niet-voorgevormde, goed "
"passende bh. De beha mag geen extra volume toevoegen. Meet uw onderborst "
"nauwsluitend en uw buste op het volste punt terwijl u de beha draagt."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bra_size_calculator.html:165
#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bra_size_calculator.html:696
msgid "Why does my bra size vary between brands?"
msgstr "Waarom varieert mijn bh-maat per merk?"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/bra_size_calculator.html:168
msgid ""
"Bra sizing can vary between brands due to different manufacturing standards,"
" materials, and fit preferences. Always try on bras when possible, and use "
"sister sizes if your regular size doesn\\"
msgstr ""
"De bh-maat kan per merk variëren vanwege verschillende productienormen, "
"materialen en pasvormvoorkeuren. Pas indien mogelijk altijd bh's en gebruik "
"zustermaten als uw normale maat niet past\\"

