#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/ip_subnet_calculator.html:244
msgid ""
"The IP Subnet Calculator is a comprehensive tool for calculating subnet "
"information, network addresses, broadcast addresses, host ranges, and "
"converting between CIDR notation and dotted decimal subnet masks. It helps "
"network administrators, IT professionals, and students understand and "
"configure IP subnets for IPv4 networks. This calculator is essential for "
"network design, troubleshooting, and subnet planning."
msgstr ""
"De IP Subnet Calculator is een uitgebreid hulpmiddel voor het berekenen van "
"subnetinformatie, netwerkadressen, broadcastadressen, hostbereiken en het "
"converteren tussen CIDR-notatie en decimale subnetmaskers met punten. Het "
"helpt netwerkbeheerders, IT-professionals en studenten IP-subnetten voor "
"IPv4-netwerken te begrijpen en te configureren. Deze rekenmachine is "
"essentieel voor netwerkontwerp, probleemoplossing en subnetplanning."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/ip_subnet_calculator.html:251
msgid ""
"Select a calculation type from the dropdown (Subnet Information, Subnet from"
" Hosts Needed, Subnet from Subnets Needed, or Convert Subnet Mask)."
msgstr ""
"Selecteer een berekeningstype in de vervolgkeuzelijst (Subnetinformatie, "
"Subnet van benodigde hosts, Subnet van benodigde subnetten of Subnetmasker "
"converteren)."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/ip_subnet_calculator.html:252
msgid "Enter the IP address in dotted decimal format (e.g., 192.168.1.1)."
msgstr "Voer het IP-adres in decimale notatie in (bijvoorbeeld 192.168.1.1)."

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/ip_subnet_calculator.html:253
msgid ""
"Enter the subnet mask in CIDR notation (/XX) or dotted decimal format "
